snippet.title: Silver Sonic: Rise of the Death Egg - OFFICIAL TRAILER (SHC2022)
snippet.description:
One robotic hedgehog double. One mad doctor. One big egg. (well, two) One archipalego of islands. One parody of a famous commercial, this is the trailer for Silver Sonic: Rise of the Death Egg.
Coming soon at the Sonic Hacking Contest 2022 in the Retro section. (Vote now!!!...in a week)

STARRING CINOSSU!!!

Link: https://shc.zone/entries/contest2022/621 (Features not only the hack, but also tons of cool bonuses and extra goodies like a JP-style box art made by me, a parody of the Sonic 1 SMS manual, and other random stuff that has no business being there like a random picture of Baldi with a bunch of Zelda 1 enemies. WOWZERS! RADICAL! GROOVY...?)

If you enjoyed, please remember to like and subscribe!

2mappers2guns (The Oldest Anarchy Community Project in Doom History):
https://doomer.boards.net/thread/2659/2mappers2guns-anarchy-community-project-edition
